summary: Only want/need one or two etc. things, but don\'t know which one they are on the BAT lists in your program files? Nirnroot? Giant\'s Toes? Ebony ingots? Diamonds? You will find them here.
descriptionHtml: Only want/need one or two etc. things, but don\'t know which one they are on the BAT lists in your program files? Nirnroot? Giant\'s Toes? Ebony ingots? Diamonds? You will find them here. Just two text files I got from here (credit and thanks goes to yoo203 for the \"mats-mats2 file, and someone else who I can\'t seem to track down now((used the GiveSkills one)) THANX!) Enjoy, this took me an entire day to do! (there are items missing, so if you know the codes, PM me with them so I can update the lists) For those interested, PM me with your question and I will answer it if I can.....still kind of a newb at this game, but I\'m getting there...
